&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead Enterprise Architecture Programs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define enterprise target-state cloud architecture and phased roadmap strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead architecture review boards and executive design discussions with client leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish reusable architecture standards, guardrails, and delivery patterns across programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Design Cloud Infrastructure&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect scalable, highly available AWS solutions using Well-Architected Framework principles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build multi-account landing zones, hybrid connectivity (Direct Connect, Transit Gateway), and DR/BC architectures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect solutions across containers, storage, networking, data platforms, and serverless computing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Automate &amp;amp; Optimize&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop Infrastructure-as-Code using Terraform and CloudFormation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create Python automation scripts and CI/CD pipelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize cloud performance, cost efficiency, reliability, and security posture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enable Client Success&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide technical guidance and mentorship to client engineering teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead workshops, knowledge transfer sessions, and incident response&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot complex infrastructure challenges and create comprehensive documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
